{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c0cc5aff0","title":"对四位外国专家的大字报的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3a8888876b","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29,"articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"15880ac4dc","type":"paragraph","text":"对四位外国专家的大学报的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"169c072d85","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月二十九日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"b69fb9d974","type":"paragraph","text":"我同意这张大字报，外国革命专家及其孩子要同中国人完全一样，不许两样。请你们考虑一下，凡自愿的，一律同样做。如何，请爵定。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"aad1664204","type":"paragraph","text":"对《关于长沙、青高、西安等地","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"82d104e254","type":"paragraph","text":"情泥报告》的批示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"694c802e21","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年九月七日）林彪、恩来、××、康生、伯达、×××、江青等同志","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"1eb6519304","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请看一看，青岛、西安、长沙等地的情况是一样的，都是组织工农反学生，这样下去是不能解决问题的。似宜由中央发一指示，不准各地这样，然后写一篇社论，劝工农不要干预学生运动。北京就没有调动工农整学生，除人民大学会调六百农民人城保郭影秋之外，其他都没有，以北京的经验告地方照办。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"91c6059ced","type":"paragraph","text":"我看×××和这位副市长的意见是正确的。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"e4a5f762d4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"8c0b9cd490","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年九月七日对署名“奥地利《红旗》派的","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"d465e71aab","type":"paragraph","text":"同志”来信的批示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"5b18ebb117","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年九月九日）退陈毅同志","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"b77cb42a15","type":"paragraph","text":"这个批评文件写得好，值得一一切驻外机关注意，来一个革命化，否即很危险。可以先从维也纳做起。请醇定。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"ade1e5cb1b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"5239ec2dc8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年九月九日精主席审查","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"6e0f428b05","type":"paragraph","text":"署名奥地利《红旗》派的同志来信。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"f87d73f134","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"},{"id":"b7cfb84371","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年九月九日270","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0"}],"page":{"id":"d74c8d38ed","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"5c0cc5aff0","start":283,"end":283}}}},"__N_SSG":true}